his clues mathematically

00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:28.020
as a system of equations.

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:30.020
What I want to do in
this video is think about

00:00:30.020 --> 00:00:32.650
whether we can solve for
this system of equations.

00:00:32.650 --> 00:00:34.970
And you'll see that
there are many ways

00:00:34.970 --> 00:00:38.026
of solving a system
of equations.

00:00:38.026 --> 00:00:39.650
But this time I want
to do it visually.

00:00:39.650 --> 00:00:41.483
Because at least in my
mind, it helps really

00:00:41.483 --> 00:00:44.780
get the intuition of what
these things are saying.

